data.lyric:
[ti:ilomilo]
[ar:Billie Eilish]
[al:WHEN WE ALL FALL ASLEEP, WHERE DO WE GO?]
[by:]
[offset:0]
[00:00.00]ilomilo - Billie Eilish
[00:02.37]Lyrics by：Billie Eilish O'Connell/Finneas O'Connell
[00:04.75]Composed by：Billie Eilish O'Connell/Finneas O'Connell
[00:07.13]Told you not to worry
[00:10.75]But maybe that's a lie
[00:15.03]Honey what's your hurry
[00:19.05]Won't you stay inside
[00:22.85]Remember not to get too close to stars
[00:26.78]They're never gonna give you love like ours
[00:31.99]Where did you go
[00:33.36]I should know but it's cold
[00:35.31]And I don't wanna be lonely
[00:37.48]So show me the way home
[00:42.57]I can't lose another life
[00:48.10]Hurry I'm worried
[00:54.79]The world's a little blurry
[00:58.80]Or maybe it's my eyes
[01:02.87]The friends I've had to bury
[01:06.78]They keep me up at night
[01:10.44]Said I couldn't love someone
[01:12.79]'Cause I might break
[01:15.08]If you're gonna die not by mistake
[01:19.53]So where did you go
[01:21.31]I should know but it's cold
[01:23.40]And I don't wanna be lonely
[01:25.48]So tell me you'll come home
[01:30.54]Even if it's just a lie
[01:34.76]I tried not to upset you
[01:36.95]Let you rescue me the day I met you
[01:41.02]I just wanted to protect you
[01:46.84]But now I'll never get to
[01:52.01]Hurry I'm worried
[02:08.01]Where did you go
[02:09.30]I should know but it's cold
[02:11.28]And I don't wanna be lonely
[02:13.49]Was hoping you'd come home
[02:18.53]I don't care if it's a lie
data.trans:
[ti:ilomilo]
[ar:Billie Eilish]
[al:WHEN WE ALL FALL ASLEEP, WHERE DO WE GO?]
[by:]
[offset:0]
[00:00.00]//
[00:02.37]//
[00:04.75]//
[00:07.13]告诉过你 不用担心
[00:10.75]也许 这不过是个谎言
[00:15.03]亲爱的 你急什么呀
[00:19.05]为何不呆在家里
[00:22.85]记住不要太靠近那些优秀的人
[00:26.78]他们可不会像我这样爱你
[00:31.99]你去了哪里
[00:33.36]我应该知道的 天气好冷
[00:35.31]我不想一个人孤零零地呆着
[00:37.48]所以带我回家吧
[00:42.57]我不能让自己陷入险境
[00:48.10]快一点 我好担心
[00:54.79]世界有点模糊不清
[00:58.80]也许是我的眼睛看不清楚
[01:02.87]我把自我埋葬
[01:06.78]内心的想法让我彻夜难眠
[01:10.44]我不会再爱上任何人
[01:12.79]因为我不想受伤
[01:15.08]所以对你死心 是迟早的事
[01:19.53]你去了哪里
[01:21.31]我应该知道的 天气好冷
[01:23.40]我不想孤零零地一个人呆着
[01:25.48]所以告诉我 你会回来的
[01:30.54]就算是谎言也好
[01:34.76]我试图不去纠缠你
[01:36.95]你我相遇之时 你拯救了我
[01:41.02]我只想保护你
[01:46.84]可如今 我再也无法保护你
[01:52.01]快一点 我好担心
[02:08.01]你去了哪里
[02:09.30]我应该知道的 天气好冷
[02:11.28]我不想一个人孤零零地呆着
[02:13.49]我一直盼望你回家
[02:18.53]我不在乎这是不是谎言
